724
01:26:56,019 --> 01:26:58,817
I was never killed with Mother.
我没有跟妈妈一起被杀

725
01:26:58,889 --> 01:27:02,086
I was ransomed by La Salle and brought to Florence...
鲍勃付了赎金 把我送到佛罗伦萨

726
01:27:02,159 --> 01:27:04,855
where I lived with Mrs. Portinari.
跟波蒂拉尼太太住在一起

727
01:27:04,928 --> 01:27:08,557
I was raised believing you killed Mother.
他们从小教育我 是你杀了我妈妈

728
01:27:08,632 --> 01:27:12,728
I hated you. I lived for the day when I could revenge her.
我恨你 我生活的唯一目的 是为妈妈报仇

729
01:27:13,337 --> 01:27:16,534
Then La Salle came to me with his plan to swindle the land from you...
然后鲍勃来找我 让我帮他从你手中骗那块地

730
01:27:16,607 --> 01:27:18,541
and I got my chance.
我抓住了这个机会

731
01:27:27,217 --> 01:27:29,981
But you were not like he said.
但你不像他说的那样

732
01:27:30,053 --> 01:27:31,987
I never thought I would...
我从没想到

733
01:27:33,290 --> 01:27:34,621
love you.
会爱上你

734
01:28:42,893 --> 01:28:45,760
Ladies and gentlemen, we are sorry to disturb you at this time...
女士们先生们 很抱歉打扰大家

735
01:28:45,829 --> 01:28:48,889
but we have just encountered some unexpected turbulence.
飞机遇到了强烈的气流

736
01:28:48,966 --> 01:28:52,595
Would you please return to your seats immediately and...
请大家马上返回座位

737
01:28:58,842 --> 01:28:59,934
Excuse me.
请开门

738
01:29:07,517 --> 01:29:10,611
It wasn't there. The money wasn't there.
箱子里没有钱

739
01:29:10,640 --> 01:29:11,660
